Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在转学到江之岛的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和一个自称是外星人的小春相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来对钓鱼完全没有兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却陷入了被谜一样的水枪逼迫去钓鱼的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫夏树的钓鱼王子超级严格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么我就被迫和外星人同居了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}(凯特 小雪 小春)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:06.66,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(1027,613)}懊悔的电车结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs44}电车结 uni knot:电车结是浮游矶钓和路亚钓经常会用到的线结，\N其用途是将主线同子线（前导线）连接到一起。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 喝汤不能发出声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人也能喝味噌汤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢藜虾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就做给你吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 加了沙丁鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起江之岛就会想到沙丁鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这家伙吃得那么悠然自得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春来住真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙丁鱼~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶经常会做一些让人摸不着头脑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特做的饭好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候说什么都无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个水枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 猫咪好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人更可怕好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凑凑凑凑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是传说中的那对组合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人和般若吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级奇怪的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好会成为艺人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 别把我和这个怪人扯在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 我干嘛在跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想这次一定要过上正常的校园生活的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样完全就是个怪人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我嘛 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你从哥哥那里听说了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有不得不钓的鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能帮助我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方言乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 钓鱼什么的我根本就不会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪的话肯定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是走狗屎运而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之不快点钓上来的话我们就回不了母星了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很危险啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不帮我们的话会有糟糕的事情发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕的事情？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球会毁灭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救地球的就只有你了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 为什么我非得拯救地球不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 总之今天先钓一条上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条！我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没实现这个约定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就带你去天空树顶端哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,sky～～ tree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海咲姐 我们来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟 还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你绝对会放弃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想弃也弃不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 教我钓鱼嘛 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子下次再叫我王子的话真宰了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逆他的意比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 拜托了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 完全无法交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙干嘛一言不发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就跳起江之岛的舞蹈什么的 很诡异的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就教他吧 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先从钓海鲈开始学怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鲈 海产的鲈鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本的路亚钓法里 鲈鱼被称作海鲈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz23.374\pos(784,365)}海鲈:海产的鲈鱼bass（鱼）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz23.374\pos(667,188)}海鲈:海产的鲈鱼bass（鱼）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}在日本的路亚钓法里鲈鱼（スズキ）被称作海鲈（シーバスJapanese sea perch）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\pos(779,509)\frz23.479}海鲈（鱼）参照渔业。\N在日本的路亚钓法里鲈鱼（スズキ）\N被称作海鲈（シーバス）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs27\pos(779,509)\frz23.479}海鲈（鱼）参照渔业。\N在日本的路亚钓法里鲈鱼（スズキ）\N被称作海鲈（シーバス）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接叫鲈鱼不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz23.374\pos(913,505)}巴士（交通工具）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\frz23.374\pos(1024,612)}包含水上巴士，\N主要指在海上\N航行的航线及船舶。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想钓海鲈 王子 教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 小樱 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好少见啊 哥哥居然和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,yes~我们是夏树的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 这些人不过是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉 他在妹妹面前换了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从现在开始要请夏树教我们钓鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 哥哥超级厉害的 你们一定能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.44,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他笑了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救生衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上这个 掉进水里的话会浮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海钓的时候穿这个可是常识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 人类是不会游泳的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是什么东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请严格的指导我~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先提醒你们 我可是很严格的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？一块一块的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼 是从组装钓具开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓具？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}tackle只的是做一项运动或事情所需的所有道具，特指钓鱼也就是fishing tackle。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼的时候所需要的一切道具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 要把这些全部组装起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓不就是了嘛 给你钓一条
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 我只说一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先将渔线轮装在钓竿上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻起拨动架 扯出鱼线穿过导眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 解说的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在引线上装上拟饵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饵我借给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西 超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我咬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个用电车结绑好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车结？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.19,0:07:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑线的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只做一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把线头穿过这个五金件的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做一个圈 从里面绕三圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉我这松垮垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不系紧的话很容易脱落的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样的很容易断线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊 夏树再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了就做一次的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 要好好记住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也这样操纵过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正经恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果一条都没钓到的话 我该办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锵锵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你居然学得挺快的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这货 完全没学会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说他干嘛又炸毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要我再教你一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 如果钓不到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我解说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再解说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.62,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真的明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子你又钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你怎么钓不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了一个门外汉哪有那么容易钓…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.83,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又咬钩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙有引力么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上次跟你说过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把杆子立起来 冷静点 收钓线
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 海鲈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要钓上来 必须要钓一条上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要钓上来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗鳃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会赔你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好绑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电车结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你有没有好好绑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 就随便绑了下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你随便绑绑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会伤到人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼不是随便就能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟这种人一起钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候 该说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 根本没有在好好听我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微考虑一下别人的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是因为你们来拜托我教 我才来教你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么都会一事无成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 有话就说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是什么意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算再有天赋那样子也钓不了鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小春的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友是不能毁约的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也… 并不是他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了 等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像快点吃到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥牌咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃过这个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝士鳕鱼沙丁鱼球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷你型的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连两年都还不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经两年了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏树 你小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把头发剪剪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害什么羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样利利落落不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子别生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 啤酒啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不去钓鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来钓 来钓嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪不肯出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候自然就肯出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪说 无所谓跟不跟我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春你和小雪在一起开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开心？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心里感觉这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 让我很兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能让小雪为难哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为难？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪想一个人的时候就让他一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一个人静静的时候就是在思考事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是非常重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让小雪一个人呆一会儿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪会和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 肯定会成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在小雪的面前这样做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样随便做做的话 说不定会伤到别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么都会一事无成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 有话就说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉好讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没必要说到那个份上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来我对那个感到不甘心啊 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很随便
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 这个果然比较难
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上嘴好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯紧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥啊 为什么要选那个小雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我就要小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会就变怪脸 一会又毁约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你跟那个孩子一起钓鱼是不现实的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我不让小雪为难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 小雪和我就会成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等成为朋友的话绝对可以钓到鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可没那么简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样的很容易就散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎么做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个说不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 这么做的话就没摩擦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不容易散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我得系得再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪会困扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会钓鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定会钓的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像 不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔皮欧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(沙丁鱼咖喱 即将开业)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙丁鱼咖喱 放了那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在叫宇佐美君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是电车结
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我系成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不会再
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便做了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能系好那个是应该了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能教我钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫阿基拉·阿加卡·山田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天转学到这个班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经25岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.28,0:20:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家不要在意 能融洽相处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}那是鸭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个江之岛没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 我们四个人第一次聚到了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事开始运转了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个小岛的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弘大 弘大的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#03再见
